## ğŸŒ Access Publicly with Ngrok (optional)

1. Install Ngrok â†’ [https://ngrok.com/download](https://ngrok.com/download)
2. In command prompt:
   ```bash
   ngrok http 80
   ```
3. Visit the public link like:
   ```
   https://abc123.ngrok.io/AI-Based%20Chatbot%20with%20Web%20Interface/index.html
   ```

âœ… Now you can access the chatbot from **any device** on any network!

